HEADWORD: Millwork
<hw>Mill"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
shafting, gearing, and other driving machinery of mills.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The business of setting up or of operating mill
machinery.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Millwright</ent>⟦br⟧
